{"tid":514880,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］洪欣扯煙過口癮","createTime":"2017-12-31T02:30:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-02T10:38:42.000Z","uid":48905,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f20d135bcde9494bd8fbd02554d7dc669125df06","tid":514880,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T02:30:08.000Z","msg":"洪欣老公張丹峰係內地演員，長駐內地工作是常識吧，以洪欣都要嫁雞隨雞，睇住細佢9年嘅老公唔好曳曳之餘，又可以夫妻檔孖住賺人仔，登台唱歌、上節目做訪問大把嘢做。<br />\n<br />\n不過一得閒佢就會返香港，多數喺香港見到佢都係湊女。早前難得約咗親朋好友坐低吹水飲杯嘢，席間仲食煙仔輕鬆吓，明顯係趁無小朋友喺身邊，嗱嗱臨過口癮，食返夠本啦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/31/102953_122d8a4b8584d096ae2ee32bb5a859e9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F31%2F102953_122d8a4b8584d096ae2ee32bb5a859e9.png&h=907d7196&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"498c121c098074659810e87fbebc65ee19a2f6f0","tid":514880,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T02:33:18.000Z","msg":"西西西 西女人"},{"pid":"9d44de00c3e50bf3132c6dda69e1527e2cfaf410","tid":514880,"uid":49267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T02:35:29.000Z","msg":"死煙剷<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5746fb70d15c39cc3b5ebba45264fb29194484b","tid":514880,"uid":26156,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T02:46:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d7940e692d91471e7a131bb35f6069efcb2714d","tid":514880,"uid":33176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T02:51:29.000Z","msg":"唔嫁雞隨雞嫁黎把撚呀"},{"pid":"e34e80131a0ecb9eb55f3621119a0a2302ea502a","tid":514880,"uid":59976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T02:52:26.000Z","msg":"唔過口癮食黎把撚啊"},{"pid":"6761b124f77a48cfe5f5c512eba0a047d39dd220","tid":514880,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T02:53:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ea8494fbb9a37ae6da70bbdf44d1ab0ac7c2c732","tid":51